orizes transactions, and provides real-time status updates."},"ar":{"question":"How does the QRPay Payment Gateway work?","answer":"The QRPay Payment Gateway acts as a bridge between a merchant\\u2019s website or point-of-sale system and the payment processing network. It securely transmits payment information, authorizes transactions, and provides real-time status updates."}},"id":"64e48f1296317"},"64e48f2806869":{"language":{"en":{"question":"What is the advantage of using QRPay\\u2019s Developer API?","answer":"The QRPay Developer API empowers developers and entrepreneurs to integrate the QRPay Payment Gateway directly into their websites or applications. This streamlines the payment process for customers and provides businesses with a customizable and efficient payment solution."},"es":{"question":"What is the advantage of using QRPay\\u2019s Developer API?","answer":"The QRPay Developer API empowers developers and entrepreneurs to integrate the QRPay Payment Gateway directly into their websites or applications. This streamlines the payment process for customers and provides businesses with a customizable and efficient payment solution."},"ar":{"question":"What is the advantage of using QRPay\\u2019s Developer API?","answer":"The QRPay Developer API empowers developers and entrepreneurs to integrate the QRPay Payment Gateway directly into their websites or applications. This streamlines the payment process for customers and provides businesses with a customizable and efficient payment solution."}},"id":"64e48f2806869"},"64e48f3b14577":{"language":{"en":{"question":"How can I access the QRPay Developer API?","answer":"To access the QRPay Developer API, you need to sign up for a developer account on our platform. Once registered, you\\u2019ll receive an API key that you can use to authenticate your API requests."},"es":{"question":"How can I access the QRPay Developer API?","answer":"To access the QRPay Developer API, you need to sign up for a developer account on